OL,3,CLabour could strip Avanti West Coast's
OL,4,Crail contract over 'woeful service'
OL,6,FLabour has said it will urgently
OL,7,Fconsider stripping train operator
OL,8,FAvanti West Coast of its contract if
OL,9,Fit wins the General Election on 4 July.
OL,11,FShadow transport secretary Louise
OL,12,FHaigh said the company owned by
OL,13,FFirstGroup and Trenitalia, has
OL,14,Fprovided its customers with a "woeful
OL,15,Fservice" on the West Coast Main Line.
