OL,6,FOffice of Rail and Road figures show
OL,7,FAvanti had the third worst reliability
OL,8,Fof all operators across the UK in the
OL,9,Fyear to the end of March 2024, with
OL,10,F6.9% of trains ` the equivalent of one
OL,11,Fin 15 ` cancelled.
OL,13,FHowever, the agreement can be
OL,14,Fterminated with three months' notice
OL,15,Fat any point from October 2026.
OL,17,FAsked about Labour's plan to bring
OL,18,Ftrain services into public ownership,
OL,19,FMs Haigh said the parties' commitment
OL,20,Fis "to bring in those contracts as
OL,21,Fthey expire or when they are breached.
