OL,3,CLabour could strip Avanti West Coast's
OL,4,Crail contract over 'woeful service'
OL,6,F"I anticipate I will be seeking advice
OL,7,Fearly on whether Avanti has been in
OL,8,Fbreach of its contract given the
OL,9,Fwoeful service that it's been
OL,10,Fproviding to passengers down the West
OL,11,FCoast Main Line."
OL,13,FShe added: "No ifs, no buts, October
OL,14,F2026 will be the last date Avanti will
OL,15,Fhave notice of that contract (ending)
OL,16,Fbut I will ask for early advice about
OL,17,Fwhether they have already breached
OL,18,Ftheir contract and whether it can be
OL,19,Fbrought in any earlier."
